---
import BaseLayout from '@/layouts/BaseLayout.astro';

const title = 'Terms of Service | Pool Pals';
const description = 'The terms that apply when you book or use Pool Pals pool cleaning and maintenance services on the Gold Coast.';
---

<BaseLayout title={title} description={description}>
  <section class="pt-16 pb-24">
    <div class="container-narrow">
      <div class="section-eyebrow eyebrow"><span class="dot"></span>Legal</div>
      <h1 class="font-display text-[clamp(36px,4.5vw,60px)] leading-[1.04] mb-4">Terms of Service</h1>
      <p class="text-ink-mute mb-10">Last updated: June 2025</p>

      <div class="prose prose-lg max-w-none text-ink-soft space-y-6">
        <p>These terms apply to services provided by Pool Pals Pty Ltd (ABN 41 638 902 117) on the Gold Coast, Queensland. By booking a service or requesting a quote, you agree to these terms.</p>

        <h2 class="font-display text-2xl text-ink mt-10">Quotes &amp; pricing</h2>
        <p>Quotes are based on the information you provide and may be adjusted after we assess your pool on site. We will always confirm any change in scope or price with you before carrying out additional work.</p>

        <h2 class="font-display text-2xl text-ink mt-10">Scheduling &amp; access</h2>
        <p>For recurring services you nominate a schedule. You agree to provide safe access to the pool area (for example via a side gate or gate code). If we cannot access the pool on a scheduled visit, the visit may still be charged.</p>

        <h2 class="font-display text-2xl text-ink mt-10">No lock-in contracts</h2>
        <p>Our recurring plans have no lock-in contract. You can pause, change frequency, or cancel with reasonable notice. Any work already performed remains payable.</p>

        <h2 class="font-display text-2xl text-ink mt-10">Workmanship &amp; guarantees</h2>
        <p>We stand behind our work. Specific guarantees (such as green-pool recovery and equipment repair warranties) are described on the relevant service pages and confirmed in writing before work begins.</p>

        <h2 class="font-display text-2xl text-ink mt-10">Liability</h2>
        <p>We carry full public liability insurance. To the extent permitted by law, our liability is limited to re-performing the affected service. Nothing in these terms excludes rights you have under the Australian Consumer Law.</p>

        <h2 class="font-display text-2xl text-ink mt-10">Contact</h2>
        <p>Questions about these terms? Email <a href="mailto:hello@poolpals.com.au" class="text-aqua-deep underline underline-offset-2">hello@poolpals.com.au</a> or call 1300 766 572.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
